location: Oratory Church of St Wilfrid, York, North Yorkshire
method: She's Got A Fancy Hat Doubles
footnotes: Rung in celebration of the conductors graduation, and fancy hat!
The variation 117xz (St Julian Bob with a YCG Bob) is rung for the first time. The band would like to name this variation "She's Got A Fancy Hat" Doubles.
The xz call is rung for the first time. The band would like to name this call a "YCG Bob"
